rows.label: tlk70000131_10_msg0001
rows.name: You helped out my dad before, right?

rows.label: tlk70000131_10_msg0003
rows.name:
My mom and dad were so happy they
made me an extra big dinner!

rows.label: tlk70000131_10_msg0005
rows.name:
When I get big I'm gonna be strong
enough to help people, just like you!

rows.label: tlk70000131_10_msg0006
rows.name: First I gotta learn arch'ry from my dad.
